OL,3,CSouth Korean man who ate to obesity to
OL,4,Cavoid draft gets suspended sentence
OL,6,FA South Korean man who deliberately
OL,7,Ffollowed an excessively high-calorie
OL,8,Fdiet so he would become obese and
OL,9,Fdodge the army draft has avoided
OL,10,Fprison after he pledged to take up his
OL,11,Fmandatory military service.
OL,13,FThe man, who was not publicly
OL,14,Fidentified, was sentenced to one year
OL,15,Fin prison, suspended for two years, by
OL,16,Fa court in Seoul for violating the
OL,17,Fcountry's Military Service Act.
