OL,6,FThe man, whose age was not revealed by
OL,7,Fthe court, has since "expressed his
OL,8,Fintention to fulfil his military duty
OL,9,Fsincerely," the ruling said.
OL,11,FA friend who encouraged the man to
OL,12,Ftake up his radical eating regime was
OL,13,Fhanded a six-month prison sentence,
OL,14,Fsuspended for one year, for aiding and
OL,15,Fabetting the offence, according to the
OL,16,Fruling.
