OL,6,FSince the Korean War, almost all able-
OL,7,Fbodied men in South Korea have been
OL,8,Frequired to serve in the army for at
OL,9,Fleast 18 months by the time they are
OL,10,F28 years old.
OL,12,FThe requirement has long been a
OL,13,Fcontentious topic ` hundreds of
OL,14,Fconscientious objectors have been
OL,15,Fjailed over the years, according to
OL,16,FAmnesty International, many of whom
OL,17,Frefused to serve on religious grounds.
