OL,6,FIt has also interrupted the careers of
OL,7,Fmany prominent sports and music stars,
OL,8,Fincluding K-pop phenomenon BTS, which
OL,9,Fwent on hiatus in 2022 to perform
OL,10,Fmilitary service.
OL,12,FThere have been dozens of cases of
OL,13,Fyoung men who intentionally gain or
OL,14,Flose weight, feign mental illness, get
OL,15,Ffull body tattoos, or self-harm to
OL,16,Freceive an exemption, the Yonhap news
OL,17,Fagency reported in 2018. The military
OL,18,Fhas since become more tolerant of
OL,19,Ftattoos, cutting off that particular
OL,20,Fdraft-dodging loophole.
