OL,6,FThe Constitutional Court ruled in 2018
OL,7,Fthat the government must provide
OL,8,Falternative civilian roles for those
OL,9,Fwho refuse to take up arms, due to
OL,10,Freligious or political reasons.
OL,12,FBut the draft has remained
OL,13,Fcontroversial ` even becoming a flash
OL,14,Fpoint in heated gender wars. Women are
OL,15,Fexempt from compulsory conscription,
OL,16,Fand volunteer females account for only
OL,17,F3.6% of the Korean military, according
OL,18,Fto the Defense Ministry.
