OL,11,FThat has angered many men, including a
OL,12,Fvocal "anti-feminist" bloc who argue
OL,13,Fthe draft gives women an unfair
OL,14,Fadvantage in the country's hyper-
OL,15,Fcompetitive job market.
OL,17,FMany point to statistics showing women
OL,18,Fattend university at a higher rate
OL,19,Fthan men, arguing that young men
OL,20,Fshould also be able to pursue their
OL,21,Fdreams and careers.
